>Description:
When searching in a help page for specific text the hilighted hit is sometimes obscured under 
the text box.  The effect is easy to reproduce when the text is in the first line of the file, 
but also occurs occasionally when the search causes the file to scroll down.
>How-To-Repeat:
1) From the PLT Help Desk home page open the "Acknowlegements"
2) Choose Edit > Find from the main menu.  The Find dialog opens.
3) Enter "ents" and click Enter.  The hit is hidden under the dialog.
